咨询服务，以帮助他们渡过难关。 此外拳头还在旗下游戏中发起了捐款活动：《无畏契约》EX.O 系列武器皮肤和配件将于 1 月 22 日至 1 月 30 日在游戏商店内上架，并更名为「Give Back Bundle」。而《英雄联盟》则重新上架了麦林炮手的「消防队员」皮肤，销售时间为 1 月 23 日至 2 月 5 日。这些皮肤所得收益将全部捐给 Riot Games 社会影响基金，用于对加州山火的支援行动中。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-c85fab2308f26998484f55c00c6ad280_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "98 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/10072457808"}}, "attached_info": "CkEIvfLntozwnqFYEAMaCTExMjk5MDU2MCCfi7e8BjAAOBRAB3ILMTAwNzI0NTc4MDh4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "8_1737448044.678505", "card_id": "Q_8963941608", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 33}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如果拳头让你来重做提莫，你会怎么设计它的技能？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-616bcf9eda47dc0f95a5e5ca23194bdf.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "90 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/8963941608"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIvfLntozwnqFYEAMaCTExMjc2OTIwOSC3rfO7BjAAOCJACHIKODk2Mzk0MTYwOHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "9_1737448044.678741", "card_id": "Q_9374534396", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 36}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "西游记中，真假猴王难以辨别，为什么只有如来能够识破？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, 